{"title":"The number of characters, words and sentences in the text","description":"This tool allows you to get to count the number of characters, words and sentences used in the text.","content":"## Statistics in the text\r\nThis tool allows you to calculate the number of characters, words and sentences used in the text, regardless of the size of your text. You can also select a part of the text and get information only on the selected section of the text.\n\n You can also familiarize yourself with other functionality of this online [text editor](/en/editor)."}